document_data.name: Turnell's Provisions
document_data.mainbody: '''Turnell's Provisions''' was a general store located in [[Tegal's Mark]] in [[Tasseldale]] during the mid-to-late 14{{th}} century [[DR]].
document_data.Location: It was found on the north side of town, a few buildings over from a shrine dedicated to the goddess [[Chauntea]].
document_data.Services: The shop sold general goods and supplies at a 10% markup.
